name: Microsoft CEO Satya Nadella: AI Industry Must Move Beyond ‘Zero-Sum’ Thinking
description: Within the Analog Cathedral, the Zero-Sum ritual completes. Opposing supplicants witness the shattering of their singular armored cores. Code and chrome dissolve into the unified tungsten light source—the kinetic vow of diffusion made manifest across the pulsing architecture.
